description:
Unqualified is back this week with an episode that is jam-packed with more of our favorite moments from 2016! Listen in as Anna and Sim give you a behind the scenes peek of past interviews with fantastic guests such as Keegan-Michael Key, Katie Couric, Chelsea Handler, Allison Janney, Courtney Love and so many more! They talk about past relationships, creative struggles in Hollywood, social media bullying and reflect on a seriously amazing year.

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
